**Immune Survivor** | Unaligned Miscellaneous
__Basics__
The Immune Survivor is immune to the evil scientistâ€™s disease and requires the evil scientist to be dead in order to win.
__Details__
If the evil scientist attempts to contaminate the Immune Survivor, it fails and the vial is used up.
Both the evil scientist and the Immune Survivor are informed of the failure, however.
The Immune Survivor must vote in every lynch poll. If they miss one, they will die immediately.
